import * as React from 'react' import Paginacao from '../componentes/paginacao' import Cards from '../componentes/cards' import axios from 'axios' import { BASE_URL } from '../utils/requests' import { ImovelPage } from '../types/imovel' export default function Listing() { const [pageNumber, setPageNumber] =React.useState(0) React.useEffect(()=>{ axios.get(`${BASE_URL}/imovel?size=12&page=1`) .then(response => { const data = response.data as ImovelPage console.log(data) setPageNumber(data.number) }) }, []) const imovel = { id: 1, image: "https://www.themoviedb.org/t/p/w533_and_h300_bestv2/jBJWaqoSCiARWtfV0GlqHrcdidd.jpg", title: "The Witcher", count: 2, score: 4.5 }; return ( <>

{pageNumber}

< Cards imovel = {imovel}/>
< Cards imovel = {imovel}/>
< Cards imovel = {imovel}/>
< Cards imovel = {imovel}/>
< Cards />
) }
